        <mxCell id="2a0f93b5c73ef8e7-19" value="&lt;h1&gt;Redis-Master Service&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Define the name of the RC, redis-master and the ports which should be proxied.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;kubectl create -f redis-master-service.yaml&lt;br&gt;&amp;gt; kubectl get services&lt;br&gt;&amp;gt;kubectl describe services redis-master&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;strokeColor=none;strokeWidth=4;fillColor=none;gradientColor=#007FFF;fontSize=9;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=center;" parent="1" vertex="1">
