        <mxCell id="2a0f93b5c73ef8e7-23" value="&lt;h1&gt;Redis-Slave Service&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make slaves available to incoming requests via service which knows how to communicate with redis-slave.Service also load balances the requests.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;gt;kubectl create -f redis-slave-service.yaml&lt;br&gt;&amp;gt; kubectl get services&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;strokeColor=none;strokeWidth=4;fillColor=none;gradientColor=#007FFF;fontSize=9;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=center;" parent="1" vertex="1">
